Python version: 3.6.9

Install requirements:
    pip3 install -r requirements.txt

Usage: 
    python3 hdr.py --mode MODE --algo ALGO

    optional arguments:
    -h, --help   show this help message and exit
    --mode MODE  0: not using saved radiance map
                 1: using saved radiance map
    --algo ALGO  0: using Drago algorithm for tone mapping
                 1: using Mantiuk algorithm for tone mapping
                 2: using Reinhard algorithm for tone mapping

My best artifact can be generated with: python3 hdr.py --mode 1 --algo 2 